CONTEXT RightResidualTypeMismatchCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT RightResidualTypeMismatchCheck
{+ This test must fail because the right residual r\s~ requires that the join of source(r) and source(s~) exists. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION s[C*B]
RELATION result[B*C]

RULE testRightResidualFail: result = r\s~

ENDCONTEXT
